@endpoint GET /2017-08-29/jobTemplates
@desc Retrieve a JSON array of up to twenty of your job templates. This will return the templates themselves, not just a list of them. To retrieve the next twenty templates, use the nextToken string returned with the array
@optional {category: str, listBy: str, maxResults: int, nextToken: str, order: str}
@returns(200) {JobTemplates: [JobTemplate]?, NextToken: str?}

@endpoint GET /2017-08-29/jobs
@desc Retrieve a JSON array of up to twenty of your most recently created jobs. This array includes in-process, completed, and errored jobs. This will return the jobs themselves, not just a list of the jobs. To retrieve the twenty next most recent jobs, use the nextToken string returned with the array.
@optional {maxResults: int, nextToken: str, order: str, queue: str, status: str}
@returns(200) {Jobs: [Job]?, NextToken: str?}

@endpoint GET /2017-08-29/presets
